kuyo_joint` transform to `/joint_states`, and `multisense_sl_robot_state_publisher` is listening to a different topic `/multisense_sl/joint_states`.", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>in drcsim 4.0.0~3</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\"><pre><span></span>roslaunch drcsim_gazebo atlas_v3.launch\n</pre></div>\n\n\n<p>Error:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\"><pre><span></span>For frame [head_hokuyo_frame]: No transform to fixed frame [utorso].  TF error: [Could not find a connection between &#39;utorso&#39; and &#39;head_hokuyo_frame&#39; because they are not part of the same tree.Tf has two or more unconnected trees.]\n</pre></div>\n\n\n<p>due to MultiSenseSLPlugin publishing <code>hokuyo_joint</code> transform to <code>/joint_states</code>, and <code>multisense_sl_robot_state_publisher</code> is listening to a different topic <code>/multisense_sl/joint_states</code>.</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "assignee": {"display_name": "John Hsu", "uuid": "{0a186eae-abf0-4514-a951-23db5eccc286}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B0a186eae-abf0-4514-a951-23db5eccc286%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B0a186eae-abf0-4514-a951-23db5eccc286%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "https://avatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.net/557058:f3968cd3-4910-4384-8349-482a6c7889ec/5445ce6e-6273-47f0-84eb-621c86ca11cb/128"}}, "nickname": "hsu", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:f3968cd3-4910-4384-8349-482a6c7889ec"}, "state": "resolved", "version": null, "edited_on": null, "created_on": "2014-10-20T19:12:11.583759+00:00", "milestone": null, "updated_on": "2014-11-07T16:51:19.628869+00:00", "type": "issue", "id": 444}